Name: Dehaka
Description: Primal Pack Leader. Collects essence from his fallen enemies to change and grow in strength.**Can attack ground units**

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to move to the target area or follow the target unit. Moving units will not engage enemies.
Root.Name: Move

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to cancel all orders and stop moving.
Root.Name: Stop

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to stay where they are and attack enemies that are within range. Units will neither chase down enemies nor move to engage.
Root.Name: Hold Position

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to patrol between their current position and the target area. Units will attack enemies and move to engage nearby enemies.
Root.Name: Patrol

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to move to the target point, fighting nearby enemies along the way. Targeting a unit with the Attack command orders that it be attacked until it is destroyed.
Root.Name: Attack

Root.Tooltip: Dehaka leaps to the target location, dealing 0 damage to nearby enemy ground units.
Root.Name: Leap

Root.Tooltip: Dehaka terrifies nearby enemies, reducing their movement speed by 75.00% and attack speed by 25.00% for for 15 seconds.
Root.Name: Intimidating Roar

Root.Tooltip:
Instantly kill the target enemy unit to heal 5% Life and gain passive abilities based on the enemy type for 15 seconds. The cooldown is based on the amount of life the enemy has when killed.

  • Air: Gain a ranged attack
  • Armored: Gain bonus damage against armored units
  • Biological: Heal 20% life
  • Light: Gain move speed
  • Massive: Gain armor and reflect damage at attackers
  • Mechanical: Gain attack speed
  • Psionic: Explode with Psionic Energy and abilities cooldown 50% faster
Root.Name: Devour

Root.Tooltip: Quickly burrow to any visible location.
Root.Name: Deep Tunnel

Root.Tooltip: This ability unlocks at Commander Level 4.
Root.Name: Deep Tunnel

Root.Tooltip: Detect cloaked, burrowed, and hallucinated units.
Root.Name: Keen Senses

Root.Tooltip: You have unspent mutation points. Click here to spend them.
Root.Name: Evolve Mutations

Root.Tooltip: Allied units near Dehaka heal 1 life per second.
Root.Name: Primal Regeneration

Root.Tooltip: Dehaka's fiery breath scorches the earth, dealing weapon damage (0) to all enemy ground units in its path.
Root.Name: Scorching Breath

Root.Tooltip: Allows Dehaka to attack air units.
Root.Name: Deadly Reach

Lear.Tooltip: Drops the current order without performing it, and allows you to select a different order.
Lear.Name: Cancel

Lear.Tooltip:
Dehaka leaps to the target location, dealing 25 + 50% weapon damage to all enemy ground units in the area.

Level 2 - Leap range increased by 6, Damage increased to 25 + 75% weapon damage.
Level 3 - Each enemy hit also grants Dehaka 1 armor for 2 seconds.
Lear.Name: Evolve Leap

Lear.Tooltip:
Dehaka intimidates nearby enemies, reducing their movement speed by 75% and attack speed by 25% for 15 seconds.

Level 2 - Enemies affected by Intimidating Roar also cannot use abilities that cost energy.
Level 3 - Enemies affected by Intimidating Roar also have armor reduced by 2.
Lear.Name: Evolve Intimidating Roar

Lear.Tooltip:
Dehaka instantly kills the target enemy to heal 5% Life and gain passive abilities based on the enemy type for 15 seconds. The cooldown is based on the amount of life the enemy has when killed.

Level 2 - Passive bonuses last 25 seconds. Range increased by 3
Level 3 - Cooldown reduced by 20%. Range increased by 3.
Lear.Name: Evolve Devour

Lear.Tooltip: Dehaka's fiery breath scorches the earth, dealing weapon damage (0) to all enemy ground units in its path.
Lear.Name: Evolve Scorching Breath

Lear.Tooltip:
Dehaka passively heals all allied units nearby.

Level 2 - 2 life per second.
Level 3 - 3 life per second.
Lear.Name: Evolve Primal Regeneration

Lear.Tooltip: This ability unlocks at Commander Level 12.
Lear.Name: Evolve Primal Regeneration

Lear.Tooltip: Allows Dehaka to detect cloaked, burrowed, and hallucinated units.
Lear.Name: Evolve Keen Senses

Lear.Tooltip: This ability unlocks at Commander Level 5.
Lear.Name: Evolve Keen Senses

Lear.Tooltip: This ability unlocks at Commander Level 5.
Lear.Name: Evolve Chitinous Plating

Lear.Tooltip: Allows Dehaka to attack air units.
Lear.Name: Evolve Deadly Reach

Lear.Tooltip: This ability unlocks at Commander Level 12.
Lear.Name: Evolve Deadly Reach

Behaviors.Tooltip: Collect Essence from slain enemies to increase Dehaka's power. Every Essence collected heals Dehaka for 2 and grants him +0.75 maximum life.Can walk over smaller units and become Massive at level 6.
Behaviors.Name: Essence
